headline: Notice Regarding Public Announcement by Macquarie Asset Management, Prologis and FIBRA Prologis
summary: MEXICO CITY, February 25, 2026--FIBRA Macquarie México (BMV: FIBRAMQ) has been informed that Macquarie Asset Management México, S.A. de C.V. ("Macquarie"), Prologis Property México, S.A. de C.V. ("Prologis"), and FIBRA Prologis (BMV: FIBRAPL 14), have entered into a Transaction and Covenant Agreement under which Macquarie has agreed to transfer to Prologis all of its rights and obligations under the management agreement entered into between Macquarie and FIBRA Macquarie, subject to the satisfact
